Package edu.pdx.cs410J.family

Class FamilyTreeConversionTestCase

java.lang.Object
edu.pdx.cs410J.family.FamilyTestCase
edu.pdx.cs410J.family.FamilyTreeConversionTestCase
Direct Known Subclasses:
TextTest, XmlTest
public abstract class FamilyTreeConversionTestCase
extends FamilyTestCase
This is the abstract superclass that tests the conversion of a FamilyTree from one form to another. The test methods can be shared by subclasses. All the subclass has to do is override the getStringFor(edu.pdx.cs410J.family.FamilyTree) and getFamilyTreeFor(java.lang.String) methods.
